      <title>AMLO Son、内政部长赢得莫雷纳执政党重要职位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/amlo-son-interior-minister-win-top-posts-in-morena-ruling-party</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥执政党“更多党”选举即将离任的总统安德烈斯·曼努埃尔·洛佩斯·奥夫拉多尔的次子以及即将离任的内政部长路易莎·玛丽亚·阿尔卡尔德担任党内领导层的重要职务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/amlo-son-interior-minister-win-top-posts-in-morena-ruling-party</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 23:08:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国预算危机前，里夫斯誓言“不会重拾紧缩政策”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/reeves-vows-no-return-to-austerity-ahead-of-crunch-uk-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯 (Rachel Reeves) 周一承诺，英国新工党政府不会恢复保守党前任政府的紧缩政策。在连续数周警告公共财政状况严峻之后，她将转向更为积极的论述。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/reeves-vows-no-return-to-austerity-ahead-of-crunch-uk-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 21:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯向纽约市捐助者承诺援助人工智能和加密货币行业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/harris-vows-to-grow-ai-crypto-industries-in-pitch-to-nyc-donors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯承诺，如果当选，将帮助增加对人工智能和加密货币的投资，并于周日向纽约的捐助者推介她的经济议程，称其将加强创新，并注重制定保护消费者和投资者的法规。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/harris-vows-to-grow-ai-crypto-industries-in-pitch-to-nyc-donors</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 21:28:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>葡萄牙总理与反对党领袖计划就预算举行会谈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/portugal-s-prime-minister-opposition-leader-schedule-talks-on-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[葡萄牙总理路易斯·蒙特内格罗和反对党社会党领导人佩德罗·努诺·桑托斯将于 9 月 27 日举行会谈，讨论 2025 年预算，此前双方本月早些时候未能就讨论时间安排达成一致。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/portugal-s-prime-minister-opposition-leader-schedule-talks-on-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 21:15:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国总理考虑对大公司征税以控制“严重”债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/french-premier-mulls-taxing-large-firms-to-reign-in-grave-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为了弥补法国庞大的预算赤字并安抚国际投资者，法国总理米歇尔·巴尼耶 (Michel Barnier) 决定对富人和大公司征税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/french-premier-mulls-taxing-large-firms-to-reign-in-grave-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 21:12:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国国会公布临时支出方案以避免政府关门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/house-stopgap-funding-proposal-seeks-boost-for-us-secret-service</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国会领导人周日公布了一项临时拨款法案，暂时维持美国政府运转至 12 月 20 日，谈判人员希望避免 10 月 1 日政府关门，并为圣诞节前不久的资金摊牌做好准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/house-stopgap-funding-proposal-seeks-boost-for-us-secret-service</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 21:12:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普和哈里斯将在对决活动中加强经济宣传</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/harris-to-unveil-economic-policy-plans-this-week-reuters-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卡马拉·哈里斯和唐纳德·特朗普在经济问题上的争斗势必愈演愈烈，两位总统候选人计划本周就竞选活动的决定性议题之一展开辩论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/harris-to-unveil-economic-policy-plans-this-week-reuters-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 19:19:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>共和党议员就报告向马克·罗宾逊施压</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/mark-robinson-black-nazi-report-brings-pressure-from-republican-senators</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日，共和党参议员对北卡罗来纳州共和党州长候选人马克·罗宾逊（Mark Robinson）的严厉报道表示担忧，并承认对唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）青睐的候选人提出了严重指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/mark-robinson-black-nazi-report-brings-pressure-from-republican-senators</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 16:51:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯里兰卡左翼政党誓言调整国际货币基金组织协议后赢得大选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/sri-lanka-leftist-wins-presidency-after-vowing-to-rejig-imf-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯里兰卡人选举了一位左翼政治局外人担任总统，谴责两年前金融危机后导致国家破产并在国际货币基金组织支持下实施严厉紧缩措施的精英阶层。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/sri-lanka-leftist-wins-presidency-after-vowing-to-rejig-imf-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 14:18:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿拉巴马州警方称伯明翰深夜枪击事件造成四人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-09-22/4-killed-in-late-night-shooting-in-birmingham-alabama-police-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿拉巴马州伯明翰（美联社）周六，在阿拉巴马州伯明翰一处受欢迎的夜生活场所，多名枪手开枪射击，造成 4 人死亡，17 人受伤，警方称这是针对其中一名被杀害者进行的有针对性的“射击”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-09-22/4-killed-in-late-night-shooting-in-birmingham-alabama-police-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 07:25:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
